---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro'
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro'

const lastUpdated = 'June 26, 2025'
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Terms of Service"
    description="Terms of Service for Modrex, the free and open-source desktop mod manager."
>
    <Nav />
    <main class="legal-page">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="prose">
                <p class="eyebrow">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
                <h1>Terms of Service</h1>

                <p>
                    Modrex is a free, open-source desktop application for managing game mods. By
                    using Modrex you agree to these terms.
                </p>

                <h2>1. Use at your own risk</h2>
                <p>
                    Modrex is provided <strong>"as is"</strong> without warranties of any kind. Installing,
                    enabling, or managing mods may affect your game, save files, or online status. You
                    are solely responsible for any consequences of using mods with your games.
                </p>

                <h2>2. Mod content</h2>
                <p>
                    Modrex does not host, distribute, or endorse any mods. All mod files are
                    downloaded from <a href="https://modworkshop.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                        >modworkshop.net</a
                    > or other third-party sources at your direction. You are responsible for ensuring
                    that the mods you install comply with the terms of service of the relevant game publisher
                    and the original mod author's license.
                </p>

                <h2>3. Open source</h2>
                <p>
                    Modrex is released under the <a
                        href="https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener">MIT License</a
                    >. The source code is available on <a
                        href="https://github.com/modrexio/modrex"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener">GitHub</a
                    >. You may use, modify, and distribute it in accordance with that license.
                </p>

                <h2>4. No affiliation</h2>
                <p>
                    Modrex is an independent project and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or
                    sponsored by any game studio, publisher, or platform.
                </p>

                <h2>5. Availability</h2>
                <p>
                    We make no guarantees about the availability or continuity of Modrex or any
                    associated services. We may update, suspend, or discontinue any part of the
                    project at any time.
                </p>

                <h2>6. Changes</h2>
                <p>
                    We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of Modrex after changes are
                    posted constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
                </p>

                <h2>7. Contact</h2>
                <p>
                    Questions or concerns? Open an issue on <a
                        href="https://github.com/modrexio/modrex/issues"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener">GitHub</a
                    > or reach out via our <a
                        href="https://discord.gg/tenzpx8JRM"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener">Discord</a
                    >.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <SiteFooter />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .legal-page {
        padding: 80px 0 96px;
    }

    .prose {
        max-width: 680px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-tertiary);
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
    }

    h1 {
        margin: 0 0 24px;
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px);
        line-height: 1;
        letter-spacing: var(--tracking-display);
    }

    h2 {
        margin: 40px 0 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }

    p {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    a {
        color: var(--color-accent-bright);
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    strong {
        color: var(--color-text);
        font-weight: 500;
    }
</style>
